companyInfo.notes:
- Thng 10/2011: Masan Nutri-Science c thnh lp vi tn gi Cng ty TNHH Mt Thnh Vin Hoa Kim Ngn.

- Thng 11/2012: Cng ty TNHH Mt Thnh Vin Hoa Kim Ngn c i tn thnh Cng ty TNHH Mt Thnh Vin Sam Kim.

- Thng 7/2014: Cng ty TNHH Sam Kim mua 70% c phn ca ANCO.

- Cui nm 2014: Cng ty TNHH Sam Kim mua li Shika, mt cng ty c 40% c phn ti Proconco.

- Thng 1 v 2/2015: Cng ty TNHH Sam Kim, thng qua cng ty con, mua thm 13,06% c phn ca Proconco.

- Thng 4/2015: Masan Group mua li Cng ty TNHH Sam Kim, c ng kim sot hai cng ty Proconco v ANCO. Cng ty Sam Kim sau c i tn thnh Masan Nutri-Science.

- Thng 3/2016: Cng ty TNHH Masan Nutri-Science c chuyn i sang hnh thc cng ty c phn vi tn c ng k l Cng ty C phn Masan Nutri-Science.

- Ngy 23/07/2019: Masan Nutri-Science cng b i tn thnh Masan MEATLife.

- Ngy 09/12/2019: Ngy u tin giao dch trn sn UPCoM vi gi tham chiu 80,000 /CP.

- Ngy 23/10/2020: Tng vn iu l ln 3,267 t ng.

- Ngy 01/11/2021: Tng vn iu l ln 3,269 t ng.
